	  <concept id="i1120663"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">5.201</ph> General.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d324e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d331e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            As required by the Small Business Act (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15 U.S.C.637(e)</xref>) and the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C.1708</xref>), agencies must make notices of proposed contract actions available as specified in paragraph (b) of this section.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d331e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d324e38" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d331e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                For acquisitions of supplies and services, other than those covered by the exceptions in <xref href="FAR-i1120688.dita#i1120688"
                              base="i1120688"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.202</xref> and the special situations in <xref href="FAR-i1120807.dita#i1120807"
                              base="i1120807"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.205</xref>, the contracting officer must transmit a notice to the GPE, for each proposed-</p>
							              <ol id="d324e54" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d331e58" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Contract action meeting the threshold in <xref href="FAR-i1120993.dita#i1120993"
                                    base="i1120993"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">5.101</xref>(a)(1);</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d331e70" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Modification to an existing contract for additional supplies or services that meets the threshold in <xref href="FAR-i1120993.dita#i1120993"
                                    base="i1120993"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">5.101</xref>(a)(1); or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d331e82" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Contract action in any amount when advantageous to the Government.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d331e93" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                When transmitting notices using electronic commerce, contracting officers must ensure the notice is forwarded to the GPE.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d331e104" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The primary purposes of the notice are to improve small business access to acquisition information and enhance competition by identifying contracting and subcontracting opportunities.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d331e113" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The GPE may be accessed via the Internet at <xref href="https://www.fbo.gov"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">https://www.fbo.gov</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
